description.en:
$Fairlife is a Binance Smartchain (BSC) token that will use its transaction fees to fight for human rights and equality by donating to charities.
Our berlin based team consists of fully doxxed members coming from marketing, investment and IT.
Our community is very important to us. We include them in decision making and we consider and reply to every single idea or question made in our telegram group to help this project advance.
